    thinking: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1d364f4b642932d40adc9cecbfeb71f5, type: 3}
  nodes:
  - id: start
    speakerID: butler
    text: Oh, mistress Vivienne... Such a beautiful voice...
    nextNodeID: start
    choices:
    - text: "Excuse me. Are you Desir\xE9e Cahuete?"
      nextNodeID: 1
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      requiredReputation: 0
      reputationChange: 0
      onSelectedEvent: {fileID: 0}
      endsDialogue: 0
    - text: See you
      nextNodeID: 
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      requiredReputation: 0
      reputationChange: 0
      onSelectedEvent: {fileID: 0}
      endsDialogue: 1
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 2
  - id: 1
    speakerID: butler
    text: I am. And if you're here to gossip about Lady Vivienne, I have no interest
      in helping.
    nextNodeID: 2
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 2
    speakerID: lyra
    text: I'm trying to understand what happened to her.
    nextNodeID: 3
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 3
    speakerID: butler
    text: ...Then you're already kinder than most visitors.
    nextNodeID: 4
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 0
  - id: 4
    speakerID: lyra
    text: You were with her the night she died?
    nextNodeID: 5
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 5
    speakerID: butler
    text: Of course. There was a grand celebration in the manor. Music, guests, applause...
      everything was for her.
    nextNodeID: 6
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 1
    expression: 1
  - id: 6
    speakerID: lyra
    text: And her final performance?
    nextNodeID: 7
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 7
    speakerID: butler
    text: She never got to sing it. There was a short intermission before the last
      song. Ten minutes, perhaps. She left to prepare herself and never returned.
    nextNodeID: 8
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 2
  - id: 8
    speakerID: lyra
    text: Did anything seem unusual?
    nextNodeID: 9
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 9
    speakerID: butler
    text: Lady Vivienne had become fearful. She believed people were plotting against
      her. I told her she was worrying too much, but... she seemed convinced.
    nextNodeID: 10
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 2
  - id: 10
    speakerID: lyra
    text: Do you know who she suspected?
    nextNodeID: 11
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 5
  - id: 11
    speakerID: butler
    text: Laurent, sometimes. Certain guests. Even members of the staff. She trusted
      fewer and fewer people as time went on.
    nextNodeID: 12
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 2
  - id: 12
    speakerID: butler
    text: I only know one thing for certain. Lady Vivienne deserved better than what
      happened that night.
    nextNodeID: 14
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
    isImportantLine: 0
    expression: 2
